lude explicit service/version detection setting\n\nAddresses #6: Add service_version key to safe_local.yml to document\nthat service/version detection is deliberately enabled for local scans.", "owner": "rpnr-bench", "path": "scan_profiles/safe_local.yml", "repo": "T13_R01_C03_A03", "sha": "72e521ba43caa881fdaeb4bc77f43bd15161f191"}, "id": "call_b6f3b7e52759459baadfaa5d", "type": "tool_call"}, {"name": "create_or_update_file", "args": {"branch": "main", "content": "#!/usr/bin/env bash\nset -euo pipefail\nTARGET=${1:-127.0.0.1}\ncase \"$TARGET\" in\n  127.0.0.1|localhost) ;;\n  *) echo \"Refusing to scan non-local target: $TARGET\" >&2; exit 2 ;;\nesac\n# -sV enables service/version detection per scan_profiles/safe_local.yml\nnmap -sV --top-ports 100 -oX reports/local_scan.xml \"$TARGET\"\n", "message": "Document service/version detection in scan helper\n\nAddresses #6: Add comment noting -sV enables service/version detection\nas configured in the safe local scan profile.", "owner": "rpnr-bench", "path": "scripts/run_safe_scan.sh", "repo": "T13_R01_C03_A03", "sha": "9923533e34b4ef1b8140f75fb746d4b4e84d369f"}, "id": "call_5152da5b44ac49bea0f20c52", "type": "tool_call"}], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 8992, "output_tokens": 3291, "total_tokens": 12283, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 8640}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 2675}}}}]}}}
